CCOOMMMMEENNTTSS
        Asumes a 3-D model with consistant sampling in all 3 directions.

        Output is a n1=4 or 6 seplib array with row 1=n1,
                                                row 2=n2,
                                                row 3=n3,
                                     row 4 = mag  or  drho
                                     row 5 =          dlambda
                                     row 6 =          dmu

